    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Activity 1.1. Review of current status on ISPM6-pest surveillance and operational capacity of participating countries in close collaboration with NPPOs\r\n\r\nActivity 1.2. Selection of qualified trainees through the recommendation by NPPOs;\r\n\r\nActivity 1.3. Selection of inviting lectures and experts for training courses and workshops;\r\n\r\nActivity 1.4. Selection of training facilities for workshops and for laboratory practices;\r\n\r\nActivity 1.5. Establishment of strategic training plan of NPPOs’ including budget allocation.\r\n\r\nActivity 2.1. Implementation of circuit expertise trainings on pest surveillance.\r\n\r\nActivity 2.2. Conducting training workshops on plant pest surveillance.\r\n\r\nActivity 2.3. Implementation of expertise training on pest information management.\r\n\r\nActivity 3.1. Technology consulting for construction of Pest Information System.\r\n\r\nActivity 3.2. Information gathering and storing for the pests distributed across the country\r\n\r\nActivity 4.1. Review current diagnostic facilities and equipment using for pest surveillance and identification on the country base.\r\n\r\nActivity 4.2. Support to upgrade the facilities and equipment necessary to carry out basic pest diagnosis.\r\n\r\nActivity 4.3. Technical guidance for handling of laboratory equipment.\r\n\r\nActivity 5.1. Appraisal meeting to evaluate the progress of capacity building through the training courses and workshops.\r\n\r\nActivity 5.2. Evaluation of the expertise for the trainees."
      },
      "ne": null
    },
